<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color: rgb(172, 29, 16); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 253, 246);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240418/1713418298524043244.png" title="1713418298524043244.png" alt="image.png" width="598" height="266" style="width: 598px; height: 266px;"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(172, 29, 16); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 253, 246); font-size: 24px;">为了学习贯彻习近平总书记在参加江苏代表团发表的重要讲话，进一步引导学生党员同志们学深悟透精神内涵，不断加强学生党员党性锻炼，坚定党员理想信念。2023年4月18日晚7时，我院学生党支部于经济管理学院党员活动室组织学生党支部例会，会议由学生党支部组织委员黄山松同志主持，学生党员参加。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(172, 29, 16); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 253, 246); font-size: 24px;">学生感想：</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="color: rgb(172, 29, 16); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 253, 246); font-size: 24px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240418/1713418365553059434.png" title="1713418365553059434.png" alt="image.png" width="643" height="305" style="width: 643px; height: 305px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(125, 78, 45); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">吴文莉</span><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">:通过学习习总书记在参加江苏代表团发表重要讲话，我学习到高质量发展是全面建设社<span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red;">会主义现代化国家的首要任务，大力发展实体经济，推动农业发展和乡村振兴，以人民幸福安康为主体。作为一名大三学生，我们要坚定理想信念，在班上积极配合班委工作，在学院积极配合辅导员工作，积极参加学院和学校活动，学好本专业知识，选好未来就业发展方向，努力奋斗，让青春在全面建设社会主义现代化国家的火热实践中绽放绚烂之花</span></span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(125, 78, 45); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>